                                    <li>Use bright, natural lighting. No filters.</li>
                                    <li>Please do not wear makeup (unless to show makeup removal).</li>
                                    <li>Ensure the Qure Faucet filter is the main focus of the content.</li>
                                    <li>Keep backgrounds clean and uncluttered.</li>
                                    <li>In cover photos, always show the filter in use (unless agreed otherwise).
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <div class="">Content Guidelines</div>
                                <ul class="list-dots ml-10 d-flex flex-column gap-1">
